{
  "stem": "10905.3",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And sure enough--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--it was us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My dad writes-- wrote a letter, Dear Mr.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Irving, not knowing what the Irving Trust Company was.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the banks were a little different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "When Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Havas walked into that branch, people say, good morning, Mr.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Havas.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, it's like people knew who you were in those days.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "People that worked in the bank didn't work there three weeks, and they were sent out to an ATM machine.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this correspondence was started.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Havas had two brothers, and they were raised by the grandparents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were orphan-- raised by the grandparents and were very, very close friends of my father, dear friends of my father.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of them was in the motion picture business.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was the European rep for RKO, and he was stationed in Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So of course, contacts were-- and he got in contact with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He came to Switzerland.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You know, he has an American passport.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He came to Switzerland to see us where we were living in Teritet.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "His younger brother, Mike, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pardon me?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Who also--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that was good-- I mean, they [INAUDIBLE] came from [INAUDIBLE], three-- these three brothers came from [INAUDIBLE], I mean, the same town.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Havas, if you had ever seen the movie he took that last boat, that last plane.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He just got out just in time, and he got here just in time to sort of-- to save himself.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And his two other brothers were-- one was working for Disney and for RKO, so he was an American citizen.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the third one, Eugene, he was a financial advisor to FDR.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he had been here many, many, many years before the older-- the oldest.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And of course, contacts were made.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
